{"tid":1848804,"cid":5,"subCid":12,"title":"用 Amazon 買嘢喺網址加 \"smile.\" 不忘做善事","createTime":"2020-01-28T16:14:06.000Z","updateTime":"2020-01-28T16:22:43.000Z","uid":36073,"like":9,"dislike":6,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"840b4a537ae531cffa4e9315ee39ad5d146d2fbd","tid":1848804,"uid":36073,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-28T16:14:06.000Z","msg":"見大家最近咁落力去 Amazon 買嘢，不過都做漏咗樣野<br />\n就係買野順便捐錢，自己一分一毫都唔使俾多<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://smile.amazon.com\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fsmile.amazon.com&d=rcEdfnhTqGmqsB%2B6X%2FYCGWWzMblEAwKPRhfqpO9yGDY%3D&h=f0f1b458\" target=\"_blank\">smile.amazon.com</a><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/BAfQSuE.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FBAfQSuE.png&h=1fda7be0&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n乜嘢係 AmazonSmile? <br />\n<br />\n每次你買嘢, Amazon會捐出產品價值嘅 0.5% 予慈善機構。你從來都唔需要俾多錢，產品種類同普通網站一樣咁多咁齊全。既然只係加多個 &quot;smile.&quot; 又何樂而不為呢？<br />\n<br />\n有咩產品符合 Smile ?<br />\n<br />\n只要你見產品網站顯示&quot;Eligible for AmazonSmile&quot; 就得喇，其實大部分產品都可以用 Smile, 有啲訂閱補給嘅產品可能唔會有（香港人去外國網站買嘢正常都係一次過買晒）。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/7qiV3z4.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F7qiV3z4.png&h=43649bba&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n（呢款Kimberly-Clark口罩賣到55000美金，唔使諗，好多大牌子都被清貨）<br />\n<br />\n有乜嘢慈善機構？<br />\n最基本大家認識 WWF、Oxfam、Orbis都有。佢都有好多當地不同類型慈善機構，<a href=\"http://例如code.org\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2F%E4%BE%8B%E5%A6%82code.org&d=rcEdfnhTqGmqsB%2B6X%2FYCGWWzMblEAwKPRhfqpO9yGDY%3D&h=23bf4f5e\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">例如code.org</a>係推廣同資助電子教育。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/b0Y3s48.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fb0Y3s48.png&h=6a38b060&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n其他地區嘅Amazon 有冇？<br />\n暫時知道英國有，可惜日本冇。<br />\n<br />\n下次買嘢點樣用返 AmazonSmile?<br />\n直接bookmark <span style=\"font-size: large;\"><a href=\"http://smile.amazon.com\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fsmile.amazon.com&d=rcEdfnhTqGmqsB%2B6X%2FYCGWWzMblEAwKPRhfqpO9yGDY%3D&h=f0f1b458\" target=\"_blank\">smile.amazon.com</a></span> 就得啦！"},{"pid":"615a94ba253090d30a2305e4546c98435302effd","tid":1848804,"uid":307619,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-28T16:15:57.000Z","msg":"有意義<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;<br />\n<span style=\"color: teal;\"><span style=\"font-size: large;\">除咗醫護之外<br />\n垃圾政府都推緊社福界去死</span></span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: large;\">學校停 康文設施都停<br />\n啲人就湧晒去唔停嘅中心<br />\n社區爆發岌岌可危<br />\n<br />\n<ins>要求立即停止所有非緊急服務</ins></span></span><br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1845195\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1845195</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/AS4YPwC.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FAS4YPwC.jpg&h=a350fa60&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"72ccd99b284f654937b463df47eb792b1e36e74b","tid":1848804,"uid":109923,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-28T16:16:08.000Z","msg":"捐慈善機構<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"07930cd47be117344e237dffb65056643dc18e88","tid":1848804,"uid":30510,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-28T16:17:39.000Z","msg":"捐你老母<br />\n香港收皮個撚個偽善機構縮晒係你老母個閪到"},{"pid":"f05fa8b3ccbd973614fb33989b976b6cf04e68a9","tid":1848804,"uid":36073,"like":0,"dislike":3,"score":-3,"quote":{"pid":"72ccd99b284f654937b463df47eb792b1e36e74b","tid":1848804,"uid":109923,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-28T16:16:08.000Z","msg":"捐慈善機構<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-28T16:17:48.000Z","msg":"好過唔做嘅，反正自己都唔會蝕多啲<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"63230d686bf5f6